short_text_with_quiz.text_japanese:
新しい仕事を見つけるのはとても難しいです。自分のスキルや興味に合った仕事を見つけるのは簡単ではありません。オンラインで求人情報を探したり、何十通も応募したりするかもしれませんが、面接にすら呼ばれないかもしれません。これはやる気をなくさせるかもしれませんが、新しい仕事を見つけるのは時間と努力が必要なプロセスであることを忘れないことが大切です。すぐに完璧な仕事が見つからなくても、あきらめないでください。探し続け、自分の分野の人々に連絡を取り、ネットワークを作ることを恐れないでください。努力すればするほど、自分が好きな素晴らしい仕事を見つける可能性が高くなります。

初心者でなくても、新しい仕事探しは大変な作業です。どこから始めればいいのか分からず、さまざまな手順をすべて把握するのは大変です。このプロセス全体を通じて冷静で整理整頓しておくことが重要です。自分のスキルと経験をリストアップし、応募する各仕事に合わせて履歴書とカバーレターを調整してください。よくある面接の質問に答えられるように準備しておき、質問することを恐れないでください。準備をすればするほど、面接プロセス中に自信を持つことができます。

新しい仕事を見つけるのは難しいですが、不可能ではありません。忍耐強く、粘り強く、そしてこのプロセスで一人ではないことを忘れないことが重要です。多くの人が新しい仕事を探す際に同じような課題に直面します。努力と前向きな姿勢があれば、自分にぴったりの仕事を見つけることができます。

仕事を探している場合は、利用可能なすべてのリソースを活用してください。あなたの仕事探しを支援する多くのウェブサイトや組織があります。友達、家族、そしてあなたの分野のプロフェッショナルから助けを求めることを恐れないでください。ネットワークを広げる人々が多ければ多いほど、自分に合った仕事を見つける可能性が高くなります。
short_text_with_quiz.text_english:
Finding a new job can be quite difficult. It is not easy to find a job that is a good fit for your skills and interests. You might spend hours searching online for job postings, and you might send out dozens of applications, but you may not even get a single interview. This can be discouraging, but it is important to remember that finding a new job is a process that takes time and effort. Don’t give up if you don’t find the perfect job right away. Keep searching, and don’t be afraid to network and reach out to people in your field. The more effort you put in, the more likely you are to find a great job that you love. 

Even if you are not a beginner, you can still find the process of searching for a new job to be daunting. It can be difficult to know where to start, and it can be overwhelming to keep track of all the different steps involved. It is important to stay calm and organized throughout the process. Make a list of your skills and experience, and tailor your resume and cover letter to each job you apply for. Be prepared to answer common interview questions, and don’t be afraid to ask questions yourself. Remember that the more prepared you are, the more confident you will feel during the interview process. 

Finding a new job can be challenging, but it is not impossible. It is important to be patient and persistent, and to remember that you are not alone in this process. Many people go through the same challenges when searching for a new job. With hard work and a positive attitude, you can find the perfect job for you. 

If you are looking for a job, be sure to use all the resources available to you. There are many websites and organizations that can help you with your job search. Don’t be afraid to ask for help from friends, family, and professionals in your field. The more people you network with, the more likely you are to find a job that is a good fit for you.

song_lyrics.lyrics_english_translation: I couldn’t possibly be calm. It’s freezing cold in the freezer. I opened it up completely and now my feelings are all over the place. I can’t help but feel like I need to make an effort to be more organized. Maybe I need to think about the contents of the freezer before I go shopping, or maybe I should use the whole thing for something else. I’m a beginner when it comes to organizing this, but it feels like a nationwide problem! It’s not like there’s a law against it, but I feel like I need to be more thoughtful in my approach. Everything I feel is connected to my emotions. I want to try everything, I want to know it all completely. I want to understand every detail. I need to make an effort. I need to do everything I can. I want to learn. I want to find a way to be a better person. I need to be more organized. I need to learn to control my emotions. I need to be more aware of my surroundings. I need to be a better person.
